Package: ironmesh-server-node
Section: net
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Ironmesh storage server node
 Ironmesh server node for the distributed storage platform workspace.
 This package ships the `ironmesh-server-node` service binary with the embedded
 server-admin web UI.

Package: ironmesh-client
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 fuse3
Description: Ironmesh client CLI and desktop helper applications
 This package ships the public `ironmesh` CLI together with the packaged client
 applications used for desktop workflows:
 `ironmesh-config-app`, `ironmesh-folder-agent`, `ironmesh-os-integration`,
 and the internal `ironmesh-background-launcher` helper.

Package: ironmesh-rendezvous-service
Section: net
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Ironmesh standalone rendezvous and relay service
 Ironmesh standalone rendezvous service for advanced deployments where the
 public connectivity service is run separately from the storage nodes.
